title: radio response
extract: A response of ROGER is shorthand for the prowords LOUD AND CLEAR. A response of WEAK BUT READABLE ("Weak Readable" is also used) indicates a weak signal but I can understand. A response of WEAK AND DISTORTED indicates a weak signal and unreadable.
